  ('dietitian-moex-10976', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者屬於介入實驗（intervention study）？ 比較乳癌患者與對照組脂肪攝取的多寡 糖尿病人飲食遵行度（compliance）的影響因素 探討肺癌病人發病前的飲食習慣 高血壓病人使用低鈉鹽前後其血壓的變化 （請接背面） 九十三年第一次專門職業及技術人員高等暨普通考試醫事人員考試、 全一張 高等考試中醫師考試、高等考試營養師考試、高等考試心理師考試、  代號：11250 （背面） 高等考試呼吸治療師考試、高等暨普通考試獸醫人員考試試題 類    科： 營養師', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d008ab3ebbd0", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "5001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-10977', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-093-4665e2ba', 'sub-dietitian-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '在民國九十年度，全國衛生單位共舉辦了50場的減脂之旅，請問此種計畫評量的方式，屬於何種評價： 效率（efficiency）  效能（effectiveness）  效果（effort）  效力（efficacy）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d008ab3ebbd0", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "093020", "c": "112", "s": "5001", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "公共衛生營養學", "year": "093", "exam_name": "093年第一次專技醫事人員、中醫師、營養師、心理師、呼吸治療師、獸醫人員考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["answer_missing", "incomplete_options"], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
